<ul>
<li>Promise.prototype.catch</li>
</ul>
<p><code v-pre>Promise.prototype.catch</code>方法是<code v-pre>.then(null, rejection)</code>或<code v-pre>.then(undefined, rejection)</code>的别名，用于指定发生错误时的回调函数。</p>
